《超級瑪利歐 奧德賽》是《超級瑪利歐》系列中首次被[[娛樂軟體分級委員會|娛樂軟體分級委員會]]評為E10+級（10歲以上），[[電腦娛樂分級機構|電腦娛樂分級機構]]評為B級（12歲以上）<ref>[http://gameranx.com/updates/id/114237/article/super-mario-odyssey-becomes-first-title-in-the-history-of-the-franchise-to-receive-an-e10-rating-from-esrb/ Super Mario Odyssey Becomes First Title in the History of the Franchise to Receive an E10+ Rating from ESRB] {{Wayback|url=http://gameranx.com/updates/id/114237/article/super-mario-odyssey-becomes-first-title-in-the-history-of-the-franchise-to-receive-an-e10-rating-from-esrb/ |date=20200930220848 }}.Gameranx.2017-08-04.[2017-10-21].</ref><ref>[https://www.destructoid.com/super-mario-odyssey-will-be-the-first-mario-game-to-get-a-cero-b-rating-in-japan-461684.phtml Super Mario Odyssey will be the first Mario game to get a CERO B rating in Japan] {{Wayback|url=https://www.destructoid.com/super-mario-odyssey-will-be-the-first-mario-game-to-get-a-cero-b-rating-in-japan-461684.phtml |date=20201112025114 }}.Destructoid.2017-09-17.[2017-10-21].</ref>。

《超級瑪利歐 奧德賽》首个评分由英国著名游戏杂志《EDGE》给出的10分满分<ref name="edge_review">{{cite magazine | title=Play • Super Mario Odyssey | magazine=Edge| publisher=Future Publishing | issue=312 | publication-date=2017-10-12 | pages=98–100 | issn=1350-1593}}</ref>。而稍后日本著名游戏杂志《Fami通》也给出了39分（满分40分）的高分<ref name="famitsu">{{Cite web |url=http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/gaming/867864/Super-Mario-Odyssey-Nintendo-Switch-REVIEW-Famitsu-score-release-date |title=Super Mario Odyssey Nintendo Switch REVIEW: New verdict in - and it’s NOT a perfect score |last=Martin |first=Liam |date=2017-10-19 |website=Daily Express |language=en |access-date=2017-10-21 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019122506/http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/gaming/867864/Super-Mario-Odyssey-Nintendo-Switch-REVIEW-Famitsu-score-release-date |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美国著名游戏网站[[IGN|IGN]]和[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]也都給出10分滿分。北美統計整體遊戲總評分的網站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]也正式確定了《超級瑪利歐 奧德賽》獲得史上最高總評價的殊榮<ref>[http://www.gamerankings.com/browse.html All-Time Best Games] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6S3NFO81u?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/browse.html |date=20140823234541 |dateformat=iso }}.GameRankings.[2017-10-29].</ref>。

